	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Dicen que tener <tag a="50" b="2" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /> da alegría a la vida.<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Muchas gracias,<delay8 /> <tag a="110" b="3" />!</message>
