<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¿No te parece <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x12 0xcd00 0x14 0x75 0x6e 0x20 0x68 0x65 0x72 0x6d 0x6f 0x73 0x6f 0x16 0x75 0x6e 0x61 0x20 0x68 0x65 0x72 0x6d 0x6f 0x73 0x61 0x0" />
